organic.title: Simmons Cancer Center: UT Southwestern, Dallas, TX
organic.snippet: The Harold C. Simmons Comprehensive Cancer Center is one of the world's premier institutions for important and innovative basic science cancer research.

organic.title: Research: Simmons Comprehensive Cancer Center
organic.snippet: The Harold C. Simmons Comprehensive Cancer Center is a “matrix” cancer center, which fosters routine interaction across scientific disciplines.

organic.title: Simmons Cancer Center | Dallas, Texas
organic.snippet: Simmons Cancer Center at UT Southwestern Medical Center at RedBird offers state-of-the-art, specialized cancer care and general hematology services.
